                "caption": "Figure 3:Qualitative Results of Egocentric Hand Reconstruction.ReViV learns robust spatiotemporal motion priors to generate plausible hand motions, even under severe occlusion or when the hands are out of view. We visualize sampled, non-consecutive frames across two distinct sequences to demonstrate temporal stability.",
