                "caption": "Figure 7:Qualitative visualization of egocentric body motion reconstruction.ReViV achieves state-of-the-art reconstruction accuracy and semantic alignment using purely monocular egocentric video input. Unlike recent baselines that produce unrealistic ego-body motions when state-of-the-art camera pose estimations (VIPE) fail (top), our approach implicitly learns the joint distribution without relying on explicit camera tracking. This allows our model to produce high-fidelity motions that surpass recent baselines, even when they are given the advantage of ground-truth camera trajectories (bottom).",
